item.title: CVE-2023-0900|2024-08-02T05:24:34.697Z -- unknown -- pricing%20table%20builder
item.description: The Pricing Table Builder WordPress plugin through 1.1.6 does not properly sanitise and escape a parameter before using it in a SQL statement, leading to a SQL injection exploitable by high-privilege users such as admins.
